{"tid":1264440,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"徵文宣！！！！送濱事件","createTime":"2019-06-28T16:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T08:44:47.000Z","uid":135810,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"459595a98cc0cc4154ee92ec72ffda2864e3a700","tid":1264440,"uid":135810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"送濱事件絕對係上佳既彈藥<br />\n<br />\n文宣可以帶風向<br />\n<br />\n中環地皮價格 香港樓價 土地不足（明日大嶼洗費；另一方面卻割地）<br />\n<br />\n從生活同錢 著手宣傳<br />\n<br />\n對果啲話香港係中國既人  強調此舉對香港無益 解放軍駐果個位根本保護唔到香港 反而 令香港人生活質素下降 用既錢上升 <br />\n<br />\n重點目標：中立人士 廢老 甚至係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n針唔吉到肉唔知痛 用主權問題去講佢地只會覺得中國要香港有咩問題 要講比佢地聽 呢個行動 對中國對香港對自己都無好處 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為正常人 71都已經會預左要上街 明白緊發生咩事 <br />\n係時候令藍絲分化 將焦點由屌示威者轉向政府</span></span>"},{"pid":"3816ced75e4e65d6a20916558b7a47d0d986b91c","tid":1264440,"uid":135810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"181a96da6acdbaad7308d5e21eba79fd5de900c4","tid":1264440,"uid":135810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"769001f8895b70051006a280fd21f6020fcf3084","tid":1264440,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"23941f4e6f11775f8c841e11d32fa6375f5bcca1","tid":1264440,"uid":51319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047f54c965879cd5f20d2478c669196595b51f5d","tid":1264440,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a341d0fc865743c6b86b6b2ef5e16c90447ca8cf","tid":1264440,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T1